data.description: Welcome to this turn key, pool home, no HOA, no rental restrictions. The property has a beautiful open floor plan and modern design. Offering over 2000 sqft of living space. Oversized corner lot with long driveway. Stainless steel appliances and granite counter tops. Large backyard with pool and covered patio area. This home offers a new Roof from 2021, new Appliances, new water softener, the water heater is just 3 years old, resurfaced pool, pool pump 2 years old, well pump motor 2 years, newly painted inside and out, new tiles, new toilets, sinks and fixtures, new counter tops and landscaping. Also not far from Disney parks. The perfect home for a family or friends to stay short or long term.
